{"tid":1613161,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"推到屯門街坊見到","createTime":"2019-10-02T12:51:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-02T15:37:31.000Z","uid":33381,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"d537aa501fa5a7c892bf7e4d63088bc6bae2b2e3","tid":1613161,"uid":33381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T12:51:48.000Z","msg":"啱啱喺屯市嘅手足就知<br />\n街坊影相/拎住電話都即刻俾人好惡咁鬧<br />\n<br />\n希望咁多位街坊唔好嬲我哋班手足<br />\n大家10.1一役大家又攰 對於鏡頭又敏感<br />\n我喺呢度鄭重咁同各位無心影大頭嘅街坊同手足道歉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實手足們俾人影咗大頭 <br />\n所承受嘅後果可能俾你地想像中嚴重<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但我應承你地<br />\n我下次再見到類似事件一定盡我所能去了解 <br />\n慢慢同手足解釋返唔好阻人影相 <br />\n好唔好？<br />\n非常非常抱歉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n亦同時希望手足如果唔想俾人影就保護好自己好冇？<br />\n錫曬你地啊 <br />\n不完美 需改善！"},{"pid":"3effee356b547e2d350a1a42299b9f049a825a2b","tid":1613161,"uid":33381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T12:52:24.000Z","msg":"自推<br />\n點都唔割<br />\n要改善"},{"pid":"32e4ca3f7f9b78d8eff5c546e809633f8bf6e2fa","tid":1613161,"uid":60563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T12:54:18.000Z","msg":"屯門手兄俾啲禮貌啦<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1612973\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1612973</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n你在場就幫手提<br />\n有人屌緊了"},{"pid":"562b5a967e124abd85f16974fba7267e0a1d1bea","tid":1613161,"uid":33381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"32e4ca3f7f9b78d8eff5c546e809633f8bf6e2fa","tid":1613161,"uid":60563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T12:54:18.000Z","msg":"屯門手兄俾啲禮貌啦<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1612973\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1612973</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n你在場就幫手提<br />\n有人屌緊了"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T12:55:34.000Z","msg":"唔係想屌啊<br />\n大家敏感我明白 只希望屯門嘅同路人見到<br />\n唔好介意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbb7c5246231779d5524577902c2884abbdd3ecb","tid":1613161,"uid":53612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T12:56:39.000Z","msg":"小心包好 先<br />\n小心 休班警 尋仇"},{"pid":"4a72e66233f6ed7d0ae4b939cc571c3e2ebc5018","tid":1613161,"uid":167928,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T12:57:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />講咗三個月要俾d禮貌"},{"pid":"9eccfbe3f9b36df603049ebe4dbe2f65839005f9","tid":1613161,"uid":33381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T13:00:16.000Z","msg":"仲有八區集結<br />\n屯門要人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"daa7e82d81c8caf3413b2106c7310945f5705903","tid":1613161,"uid":301479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T13:00:48.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"6fa923b2e986db9aca3130ec4d773da1dcc5ffbf","tid":1613161,"uid":33381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T13:01:44.000Z","msg":"街坊唔好嬲佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n手足有時口直心快 都係出於擔心同路人被影"},{"pid":"f6fd840331de393dfe88d98e93cd8c677aa62ba9","tid":1613161,"uid":62151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T13:02:36.000Z","msg":"十八銅人<br />\n一邊打一邊做PR 軟硬兼施<br />\n==========<br />\n今次我地好彩有美國幫手<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">咁下次呢?</span><br />\n確保槍權先算係香港人嘅最終勝利<br />\n嫌太長直接睇#3<br />\n<br />\n[長文]香港警察的清算及其暴動的可能性，真普選是否足夠，防止暴政再現及港人槍權<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1612769\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1612769</a>"},{"pid":"a85f6ec91f1de35cbd1cbcee4faf356fcfc91aad","tid":1613161,"uid":33381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T13:03:27.000Z","msg":"仲有今次手足係惡咗啲<br />\n但作為同路人就唔好再屌啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n相信屯門寶寶下次會做返好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ea371f4239a7d2102a9f185533d899c35bdd796","tid":1613161,"uid":38548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T13:04:01.000Z","msg":"唔係想分化<br />\n<br />\n但發覺我識得有D真前線勇武手足反而唔會咁惡屌人<br />\n<br />\n因為佢地都知抗爭需要公關<br />\n<br />\n明明佢地係最驚俾人影大頭個班<br />\n<br />\n唔好亂屌街坊呢樣野真係講左三個月有多喇"},{"pid":"ace50e64edf57aea53cf73123f0c11efc75da6ac","tid":1613161,"uid":167340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T13:04:15.000Z","msg":"Push<br />\n落去派傳單同道歉好似實際啲<br />\n誠意有先"},{"pid":"e7d921dd9978f676ad90bc1017099f194a6cb826","tid":1613161,"uid":33381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T13:06:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/w4WrYCX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fw4WrYCX.jpg&h=d7ac0866&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fwLo0Ru.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfwLo0Ru.png&h=bd19ee36&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9f3c204561b453371f0afa7349e90f9e299c0fe5","tid":1613161,"uid":33381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ace50e64edf57aea53cf73123f0c11efc75da6ac","tid":1613161,"uid":167340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T13:04:15.000Z","msg":"Push<br />\n落去派傳單同道歉好似實際啲<br />\n誠意有先"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T13:08:46.000Z","msg":"我覺得又over咗 有啲左膠feel<br />\n下次手足留意返就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋希望屯門嘅街坊，叔叔嬸嬸唔好介意 唔好擺喺心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4826af1e8cca1ddff5ac8f9eced13ebfaa5f71b4","tid":1613161,"uid":33381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5ea371f4239a7d2102a9f185533d899c35bdd796","tid":1613161,"uid":38548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T13:04:01.000Z","msg":"唔係想分化<br />\n<br />\n但發覺我識得有D真前線勇武手足反而唔會咁惡屌人<br />\n<br />\n因為佢地都知抗爭需要公關<br />\n<br />\n明明佢地係最驚俾人影大頭個班<br />\n<br />\n唔好亂屌街坊呢樣野真係講左三個月有多喇"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T13:10:27.000Z","msg":"大家敏感同想保護手足姐 <br />\n係愛！<br />\n相信下次大家會做返好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n正所謂做人冇公關 食屎嫁啦 <br />\n你睇下班黑警<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71410b093fd9d9682ae76f579dfc0e6aad39d627","tid":1613161,"uid":33381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T13:15:41.000Z","msg":"怕失民意嘅手足<br />\n<br />\nFrom fb gp真&middot;屯門友嘅一個post：<br />\n剛行過市中心 <br />\n原來已經唔可以影相 都啱既 <br />\n尊重他們 提提各位 行過路過<br />\n唔好影相 尊重他人<br />\n<br />\n所以真正嘅同路人其實就會明<br />\n唔洗太擔心<br />\n但一般公關都要做返好<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c69c6e9f3589b61bcea0ca31474a566c8503a221","tid":1613161,"uid":33381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T13:25:58.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"5342612cc095dfc269c1451c21ef3086f678f667","tid":1613161,"uid":139915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T13:28:23.000Z","msg":"你係連登講都無乜用<br />\n有誠意啲今晚/聽日掛張紙上心口say sorry<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢地通常會理解返"},{"pid":"bdef1e189b42d59559c5abf4fa28fbc5912d2dd1","tid":1613161,"uid":3501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T13:44:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca2287fdd51b4ceb6af07cedd246629a8c7c332c","tid":1613161,"uid":283755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6fa923b2e986db9aca3130ec4d773da1dcc5ffbf","tid":1613161,"uid":33381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T13:01:44.000Z","msg":"街坊唔好嬲佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n手足有時口直心快 都係出於擔心同路人被影"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T13:57:51.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">做文宣大家不防帶帽帶口罩點都要保護自己，我哋又唔係死黑警同班廢老藍絲。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">唔需要同街坊樹敵始終多個朋友好過多個敵人</span>"},{"pid":"68d3ee9bf7b0bad4f548e33370eee1b8b964ae49","tid":1613161,"uid":247930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T15:37:31.000Z","msg":"其實有啲叔叔嬸嬸唔係想影啲手足大頭<br />\n佢哋只係想影現場情況<br />\n我見到有個叔叔係影緊啲手足好努力摺紙鶴<br />\n結果被人好大聲咁鬧走咗<br />\n希望各位手足保持理性<br />\n唔好連支持我哋嘅民意都消失埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}